Pintu kecemasan/ Emergency exits
308023 12/83

Tall pinggang keselamatan anda
Ketika beranakat dan mendarat
tegakkan tempat duduk, pasangkan
tali pinggang keselamatan dan jangan
merokok.
Your seat belt
On take-off and landing, put your seat
upror. Tasten seal oel and do nou
smoke.
Kedudukan lekapbadan semasa
kecemasan
Ketika kecemasan bongkokkan badan
dan pegang pergelangan kaki
Emergency brace position
in an emergencu lanaia bend bodu
forward and grip ankles
Jeket keselamatan / Life jackets
Jeket keselamatan terletak di bawah tempat duduk
Life jackets are placed under the seats
Pintu kecemasan 1/Exit 11
Pintu kecemasan 2.3.4/Exit 2.3.4

Oksijen kecemasan
Pasang tali pinggang keselamatan dan jangan merokok.
Corong oksijen akan keluar secara otomatik dari barisan
kerusi, dihadapan atau dari atas.
Lekapkan corong di
mulut dan hidung, lekatkan tali pengikat dikepala anda
dan bernafas seperti biasa.
Emergency oxygen
Fasten seat belt and no smoking. Oxygen masks will drop
automatically from seats in front or overhead. Place mask
over mouth and nose, pull the elastic band over head and
breathe normally.
Corong oksijen dari kerusi dihadapan.
Oxygen masks from seat back
Corong oksijen dari atas
Oxygen masks from ceiling.
Gelungsur / Pelampung keselamatan
Slide/Raft.

properties.sfomuseum:description: Safety information card issued by Malaysian Airline System (MAS) for its McDonnell Douglas DC-10 fleet; double-sided bi-fold laminated yellow card with illustrations and text in Malay and English demonstrating safety instructions and emergency procedures.
